00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:49.000
The chapter is only for thirty minutes.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:54.000
You may think it's quite long but compared to the full game it's very short. It's a short content. 

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.000
So if we were to decide to make it in an image format, then you will just see it and thatâ€™s it. 

